2.5.mermaid:
sequenceDiagram
    participant Tool as Tool Module
    participant ESB as ESB
    participant Agent as Noor Agent
    participant FastTime as Noor FastTime
    Tool->>ESB: envelope{ intent: <enum> }
    ESB->>ESB: normalize(intent) // alias→canonical, defaulting
    ESB-->>Agent: envelope{ intent: <canonical> }
    Agent->>FastTime: tick{ extensions.intent := envelope.intent }
    Note over FastTime: CORE semantics consult intent (phase/posture); RFC-0004 only carries signal
